name: ent_wiki_sm
author: Explosion AI
description: Multi-lingual named entity recognition model trained on Wikipedia. Supports identification of PER, LOC, ORG and MISC entities for English, German, Spanish, French, Italian, Portuguese and Russian.
notes: Supported entity types: `PER`, `LOC`, `ORG` and `MISC`. Supported languages: English, German, Spanish, French, Italian, Portuguese, Russian. Because it's trained on Wikipedia, the model may perform inconsistently on many genres, such as social media text.
